• Usage: /repo-ci setup | /repo-ci learn | /repo-ci retry | /repo-ci <inherit|off|local|remote|local-and-remote> | /repo-ci issues <inherit|none|comma-list> | /repo-ci rounds <inherit|N> | /repo-ci long-ci <inherit|on|off> Use /repo-ci setup to enable repo CI for this repo, /repo-ci retry to rerun the workflow, or use the other forms to change only the current session.
